Interface VersionSource

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface VersionSource
extends NamedDomainObjectContainer<VersionSourceLanguage>
    Configuration of "main" source code or "test" source code targeting a specific version of Java. Any recognized JVM-based language can be configured
